English Version
────────────────────────────────────────

[Core Principle] Completely free for personal use; any commercial scenario
requires prior written authorization.

▌ Personal Use (No Authorization Required)

The following are permitted without contacting the author:

  · Reading or modifying the code for learning, research, or personal
    understanding
  · Running aitrack for your own development workflow on hardware or
    servers you control
  · Personal articles, videos, side projects, or content for social platforms
    (YouTube, Medium, personal blog, etc.)
  · Non-commercial demos, tutorials, blog posts, or podcasts
  · Derivative projects published under your own personal repository — with
    prominent attribution in the README:
    Derived from MapleEve/company-aitrack

▌ Commercial Use (Prior Written Authorization Required)

The following require written authorization from the author before proceeding:

  · Any company, team, studio, or organization integrating this project into
    internal tooling or external-facing products
  · Delivering technical services to paying clients using this project as a
    foundation (outsourcing, B2B SaaS, consulting, etc.)
  · Building commercial software products, paid subscriptions, or paid hosting
    services based on this project
  · For-profit training courses, workshops, or paid communities
  · Using output or code from this project in work-for-hire deliverables

▌ Authorization Contact

WeChat Official Account: 等枫再来

────────────────────────────────────────
中文版 · Chinese
────────────────────────────────────────

【核心原则】个人使用完全免费；任何商业场景须事先取得书面授权。

▌ 个人使用（无需授权）

下列情形可直接使用，无需联系作者：

  · 学习、研究、自我理解目的的代码阅读与修改
  · 在自己控制的硬件或服务器上，为个人开发工作流运行 aitrack
  · 个人文章、视频、副业或社交媒体内容创作（小红书、公众号、B站等）
  · 以非营利为目的发布的 demo、教程、博客、播客
  · 在个人仓库发布的派生项目——须在 README 显著位置标注来源：
    Derived from MapleEve/company-aitrack

▌ 商业使用（须事先取得书面授权）

下列情形必须联系作者获得书面授权，方可进行：

  · 企业、团队、工作室或机构将本项目纳入内部工具链或对外产品
  · 以本项目为基础向付费客户交付技术服务（外包、B 端 SaaS、咨询等）
  · 基于本项目构建商业软件、付费订阅或付费托管服务
  · 以营利为目的开设的培训课程、工作坊或付费社群
  · 在商单（乙方向甲方交付物）中使用本项目生成的内容或代码

▌ 授权联系

微信公众号：等枫再来

